<br>
Considering my success record with the dragons, the amount of resistance needed really varies depending on how good the raid team is.  I'm currently 23-3 with Vox, and 26-4 with Nagafen.<br>
<br>
Group structure and timing counts for a lot.  The Kunark dragons are another matter entirely.<br>
