Thanks for the feedback, knowledge from experience is most valuable, if it comes from good sources. These are good sources for sure. Some people have messed up conceptions of the levels that other classes can do things because they don't understand other classes fully, like the people who told me that HG's are too high for me to hunt solo below 44, or that I can't solo Avocets at 25, or that I can't kill Dorn at 15. However, if Vox and Naggy are 55, that's a different story. Nekoj is right. I've had trouble landing spells on mobs that are 8 or more levels above me. I think I'll wait then, unless I find out otherwise. Thanks all...<br>
